# CADEX DECISIONS.log — append-only architectural decision record
# Never edit or delete past entries. Only append.
# Agent loads: last 10 entries + keyword-matched entries for current task.
# Full history is never loaded — only retrieved by match.
#
# CONFIDENCE levels:
#   confirmed   — verified by test, code, or explicit user decision
#   provisional — working assumption, not yet verified
#   speculative — hypothesis under consideration, do not treat as truth
#
# SOURCE values:
#   user        — explicitly stated by the developer
#   test        — proven by passing/failing tests
#   code        — inferred from existing implementation
#   discussion  — emerged from planning conversation
#   inference   — agent-inferred, needs verification

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SCHEMA — copy this block for every new decision
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ---
# date:             YYYY-MM-DD
# decision:         [one sentence — what was decided]
# reason:           [why — what was considered and rejected]
# affects:          [file paths or system areas impacted]
# confidence:       confirmed | provisional | speculative
# source:           user | test | code | discussion | inference
# last_verified_at: YYYY-MM-DD | null
# keywords:         [comma-separated terms for retrieval matching]
# ---

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# EXAMPLE ENTRIES (delete and replace with your own)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

